When a user initially loads the Patient Mappings screen, section 8.1.15.1 Mappings for FiveWs Pattern (                             ) appears without displaying the link between the brackets.  When the user hovers over the bracket, the link (http://hl7.org/fhir/fivews) appears

Suspect the root cause may be this CSS:
.self-link-parent a {
    visibility: hidden;
}

When a user initially loads the Patient Mappings screen, section 8.1.15.3 Mappings for LOINC code for the element (                  ) appears without displaying the link between the brackets.  When the user hovers over the brackets, the link (https://loinc.org/) appears

Suspect the root cause may be this CSS:
.self-link-parent a {
    visibility: hidden;
}
